name: The lynx's paw
description:
"The lynx's paw" and "The murder of the poacher" are a duo paintings, they communicate about horrors made to Eurasian lynxes in my home region, Franche-Comté. As we are approaching winter Eurasian lynxes starts having more activities in the region because there are fewer people outside. It is also, unfortunately, the moment when poachers hunt this magnificent endangered species.

Size: 2.13Mb
Format: JPEG 2022x2022
Year: 2021
